Subject Re Date is stuck From Mel White With your date time problems, you MIGHT have a problem with the Dallas Clock Chip I'm making a possibly bad assumption that your system has a clock chip and that it's the standard Dallas Clock Chip I always look at the battery and the clock chip when such things go wrong at least, as the first course of action Mel White Data Services City of Garland, Texas Mel White Two Ravens BBS ASP Member BBS Fidonet Your Window To The World MBAS